OL,3,CRiver Action begin legal challenge to
OL,4,CNRW after chicken farm expansions
OL,6,FEnvironmental charity River Action has
OL,7,Flaunched a legal challenge against
OL,8,FNatural Resources Wales after it
OL,9,Fapproved the expansion of three
OL,10,Fpoultry farms in Powys.
OL,12,FThey've accused the regulator of
OL,13,F"washing its hands of manure pollution
OL,14,Fby taking an unlawfully narrow view of
OL,15,Fits powers."
OL,17,FThe case focuses on whether NRW is
OL,18,Fproperly using its role as
OL,19,Fenvironmental regulator to prevent
OL,20,Fpollution from intensive farming.
