OL,3,CRiver Action begin legal challenge to
OL,4,CNRW after chicken farm expansions
OL,6,FIn November 2025 NRW approved permit
OL,7,Fvariations allowing three intensive
OL,8,Fpoultry units to expand in Powys.
OL,10,FRiver Action argue that in doing so,
OL,11,FNRW proceeded on the basis that the
OL,12,Fenvironmental impacts of manure, that
OL,13,Fmay leave farms and enter rivers like
OL,14,Fthe Wye and the Severn, would be
OL,15,Foutside of the regulator's control.
OL,17,FRiver Action says that the law
OL,18,Frequires NRW to assess and prevent
OL,19,Fpotential pollution impacts that could
OL,20,Farise if manure is exported off-site.
