OL,6,FRiver Action's Head of Legal, Emma
OL,7,FDearnaley said "Pollution from
OL,8,Fintensive poultry farming doesn't stop
OL,9,Fat the farm boundary, and regulation
OL,10,Fcan't lawfully stop there either.
OL,12,F"NRW has treated the boundary of the
OL,13,Finstallation as the boundary of its
OL,14,Fregulatory responsibility, even though
OL,15,Fthe environmental harm caused by
OL,16,Fexcess manure occurs well beyond that
OL,17,Fline."
