OL,3,CRiver Action begin legal challenge to
OL,4,CNRW after chicken farm expansions
OL,6,F"If the regulator assumes someone else
OL,7,Fwill deal with manure pollution
OL,8,Fwithout securing meaningful
OL,9,Fsafeguards, rivers like the Wye and
OL,10,Fthe Severn will continue to decline."
OL,12,FRiver Action is asking the court "to
OL,13,Fdeclare that NRW's interpretation of
OL,14,Fits powers was wrong, make clear NRW
OL,15,Fmust lawfully assess and regulate
OL,16,Fmanure-related impacts through
OL,17,Fenvironmental permitting where they
OL,18,Fare a consequence of the permitted
OL,19,Factivity, and quash the three Powys
OL,20,Fpermit decisions."
