OL,6,FCabinet Secretary for Rural Affairs
OL,7,FHuw Irranca-Davies said he cannot
OL,8,Fcomment on individual cases, but
OL,9,Fadded, "where we are absolutely
OL,10,Ffocused is on cleaning up the quality
OL,11,Fof our rivers, there is a real issue
OL,12,Fhere, and that includes where you have
OL,13,Fcontaminates from chicken farms,
OL,14,Fthat's why we've brought forward the
OL,15,Fgreen paper on a clean water bill.
